    "causal_summary": "The 13-iteration peck-source deep-research pass (cross-model verified by MiniMax M3) found a coherent \"peck verification discipline\" bundle implemented in peck's agent prompts that the 2026-06-02 README pass missed entirely. This packet adopts that bundle as five rules: completion-verdict freshness binding (T6, the anchor), implementer escalation gates (T5), anti-verdict-softening (T7), reviewer read-budget discipline (T8), and a docs-only numeric-severity calibration note (T9). All changes land on agent/skill prompts, the completion gate, and CLAUDE.md/AGENTS.md, with zero overlap with the 027 memory phases 002-008.",
